    "en": {
      "title": "Young girl killed in Velawatha train collision: Sister injured",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two young women were hit by a train near the police station yesterday evening.",
        "The two young women met with an accident in the train traveling to Aluthgama at the Colombo-Fort railway station.",
        "Both the young women have been identified as siblings and hail from Udappussalawa area."
